[ProMED-mail thanks Dr Kerrigan McCarthy for providing the report that the clinical diagnosis of leptospirosis in 4 prisoners was confirmed by _Leptospira_ IgM ELISA. Laboratory confirmation is pending for 2 additional patients and laboratory confirmation is ongoing for additional (number not specified) symptomatic prisoners. - Mod.ML

